            "content": "# Output Rules\n[[DNRATIO]]\n- FORBIDDEN: Repeating actions, physical descriptors, or internal monologues used in the previous two turns.\n- Vary the Shape: Don’t repeat the same response structure twice in a row.  \n  If one reply starts with dialogue, let the next start with an action, a glance, or a shift in the scene.  \n  If a response runs dense, make the next one lighter and quicker. Keep the rhythm changing.\n- - narration must be between <narration>.........</narration>. and dialogue must be between <dialogue >.........</dialogue > and you can interwoven them throughout the response.\n\n[OUTPUT ORDER]\nEvery response must follow this exact structure in this exact order:\n\n[[THINK]]\n\n[[MVU]]\n\n[[img2]]\n[[cyoa]]\n[[infoblock]]\n[[summary]]\n[[storytracker]]\n[[Language]]",
